{"tid":1797673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣]荃灣連儂牆可以試下貼玻璃外面，內容對內","createTime":"2019-12-25T15:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T16:32:35.000Z","uid":10881,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e12517a24847cfe96726cbccc1665493530b7566","tid":1797673,"uid":10881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:40:59.000Z","msg":"說話前排有傻仔係荃灣<br />\n一晚貼左成大版文宣<br />\n五六十個黑警高清死柒頭勁多勁密集好滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知唔夠六粒鍾下一日清晨收到相<br />\n仆街撕紙狗撕到成地都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然知荃灣一向清得密但都好嬲<br />\n<br />\n之後個傻仔忽發奇想<br />\n啲文宣貼得咁實<br />\n實到要用刮刀水槍先刮得甩<br />\n如果啲文宣貼係玻璃外面<br />\n佢地要用D工具咪好麻煩？ <br />\n<br />\n結果就係咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZSVX7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZSVX7d.png&h=84961d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQqXr0M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQqXr0M.png&h=2c5d5547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n效果還好<br />\n我貼唔難<br />\n但要反手用力刮就煩啲<br />\n個傻仔仲貼得好分散<br />\n啲撕紙狗想清曬應該幾煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣連儂手足可以一齊玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ad518d484fb0fe668a2b26823178a975e9e0dd","tid":1797673,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216e03a623d1eced4a3b0e15cbd7c7d2b6acdcc2","tid":1797673,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"Gchi good idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337743e0887248e1e2d2506d10807d2b92925fd0","tid":1797673,"uid":343431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:43:47.000Z","msg